  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="brand-hero">
    <div class="hero-top-stripe"></div>
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Mahathi Infotech — Brand Identity System</div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">
      Built For <span>Enterprise.</span> Designed For Trust.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">A premium visual identity system for the future of insurance technology. Every element is designed to communicate precision, trust, and modern enterprise leadership.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta-row">
      <div><div class="hero-meta-label">Document</div><div class="hero-meta-value">Brand Guidelines v2.0</div></div>
      <div><div class="hero-meta-label">Category</div><div class="hero-meta-value">Insurance-Tech</div></div>
      <div><div class="hero-meta-label">Edition</div><div class="hero-meta-value">2025</div></div>
      <div><div class="hero-meta-label">Classification</div><div class="hero-meta-value">Enterprise</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ 01 BRAND OVERVIEW ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-section section-anchor" id="overview">
    <div class="section-label">01 — Foundation</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Brand Overview</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="section-intro">Mahathi Infotech is a modern insurance-technology company redefining how enterprise organizations manage, distribute, and understand insurance. Our brand stands at the intersection of trust, precision, and intelligent technology.</p>

    <div class="overview-grid">
      <div class="overview-card">
        <div class="overview-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i></div>
        <div class="overview-card-label">Vision</div>
        <div class="overview-card-headline">To Be The Intelligence Layer Of Insurance</div>
        <p class="overview-card-body">We envision a world where insurance operates with the precision of technology and the empathy of human understanding — where every policy, claim, and decision is powered by intelligent systems that enterprises can trust.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-card">
        <div class="overview-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-compass"></i></div>
        <div class="overview-card-label">Mission</div>
        <div class="overview-card-headline">Transforming Insurance Through Intelligent Technology</div>
        <p class="overview-card-body">We build enterprise-grade insurance technology platforms that simplify complexity, accelerate decisions, and create measurable value for carriers, brokers, and policyholders across global markets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-card">
        <div class="overview-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-star"></i></div>
        <div class="overview-card-label">Brand Promise</div>
        <div class="overview-card-headline">Precision. Trust. Enterprise Scale.</div>
        <p class="overview-card-body">Every interaction with Mahathi delivers the confidence of enterprise reliability, the clarity of precise design, and the assurance of a partner deeply invested in your success.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-card">
        <div class="overview-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3"></i></div>
        <div class="overview-card-label">Brand Personality</div>
        <div class="overview-card-headline">Calm Intelligence. Strategic. Modern.</div>
        <p class="overview-card-body">Mahathi communicates with measured authority — never flashy, never generic. We are the trusted advisor: quietly confident, deeply competent, and always forward-thinking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="brand-statement-block">
      <div class="brand-statement-eyebrow">Brand Statement</div>
      <div class="brand-statement-quote">Where Enterprise Meets Intelligence.<br>Where Insurance Meets Trust.</div>
      <p class="brand-statement-body">Mahathi Infotech operates at the frontier of insurance-tech — bringing together advanced SaaS architecture, enterprise-grade security, and intuitive design to create platforms that power the most critical decisions in the industry. We don't follow trends. We establish standards.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ BRAND STORY ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-section section-anchor" id="brand-story">
    <div class="section-label">02 — Brand Story</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="section-intro">Mahathi Infotech is a trusted partner built for the unique complexities of insurance and healthcare. We exist to bring clarity, precision, and purpose to an industry that demands nothing less than absolute reliability.</p>

    <div class="story-split">
      <div class="story-block">
        <span class="story-number">01</span>
        <div class="story-block-eyebrow">Our Origin</div>
        <div class="story-block-headline">Built For The Complexity Of Insurance</div>
        <p class="story-block-body">Insurance is one of the most complex, regulated, and consequential industries on earth. Mahathi was founded to bring the discipline of modern technology — intelligent systems, clean data, and precise workflows — to the organizations that manage this complexity every day. We don't simplify what cannot be simplified. We make the complex navigable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-block">
        <span class="story-number">02</span>
        <div class="story-block-eyebrow">Our Promise</div>
        <div class="story-block-headline">Measurable Outcomes For Every Client</div>
        <p class="story-block-body">Every engagement with Mahathi is anchored in one commitment: measurable outcomes. Not vague transformations or aspirational roadmaps — but concrete improvements in efficiency, accuracy, and decision velocity that carriers, brokers, and administrators can track, report, and trust. This is what separates an enterprise technology partner from a vendor.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="promise-strip">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1rem;position:relative;z-index:1;">Brand Promise</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.6rem;letter-spacing:0.5px;color:var(--cream);line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:1rem;position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:700px;">The Intelligence Layer That Insurance Has Always Needed.</div>
      <p style="font-size:0.92rem;color:rgba(238,240,236,0.6);line-height:1.78;max-width:560px;position:relative;z-index:1;">We combine enterprise-grade architecture with deep insurance domain knowledge to create platforms that don't just process data — they generate insight, accelerate decisions, and build institutional confidence across every stakeholder in the value chain.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Logo Story -->
    <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Our Logo, Our Identity</div>
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;"></div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--cream2);border-radius:12px;padding:3rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;">
        <!-- Icon mark large -->
        <div style="width:110px;height:110px;border-radius:24px;background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--cream2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
          <svg viewBox="100 100 240 250" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:86px;height:86px;">
