  <!-- ═══ BRAND VOICE ═══ -->
  <section class="brand-section section-anchor" id="brand-voice">
    <div class="section-label">03 — Voice &amp; Tone</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Brand Voice</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="section-intro">Mahathi speaks with the measured confidence of a deeply capable partner — not a vendor, not a consultant, but a trusted intelligence. Our voice is clear, consultative, and always grounded in outcomes. We never overclaim, never oversimplify, and never resort to jargon for its own sake.</p>

    <div class="tone-spectrum">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Tone Spectrum</div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;">
        <div class="tone-axis">
          <span class="tone-label">Technical</span>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--forest2) 0%, var(--sage) 65%, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 100%);"></div>
          <div class="tone-marker" style="margin:0 -5px;"></div>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%); flex:0.4;"></div>
          <span class="tone-label">Accessible</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tone-axis">
          <span class="tone-label">Formal</span>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--forest2) 0%, var(--sage) 70%, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 100%);"></div>
          <div class="tone-marker" style="margin:0 -5px;"></div>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%); flex:0.3;"></div>
          <span class="tone-label">Conversational</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tone-axis">
          <span class="tone-label">Bold</span>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--forest2) 0%, var(--sage) 55%, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 100%);"></div>
          <div class="tone-marker" style="margin:0 -5px;"></div>
          <div class="tone-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(118,163,121,0.2) 0%, transparent 100%); flex:0.5;"></div>
          <span class="tone-label">Measured</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:1.75rem;padding-top:1.75rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(178,199,179,0.12);">
        <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage2);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Our Voice In Three Words</div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:1.25rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--cream);padding:0.5rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(118,163,121,0.12);border-radius:6px;">Confident</span>
          <span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--cream);padding:0.5rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(118,163,121,0.12);border-radius:6px;">Clear</span>
          <span style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--cream);padding:0.5rem 1.25rem;background:rgba(118,163,121,0.12);border-radius:6px;">Consultative</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="voice-grid">
      <div class="voice-card voice-do">
        <div class="voice-card-label">✓ We Say</div>
        <div class="voice-card-title">Outcome-Led</div>
        <p class="voice-card-body">We lead with results, not features. "Mahathi reduces claims processing time by 40%" rather than "Mahathi uses advanced AI algorithms."</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;padding:1rem;background:var(--cream);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--forest);font-style:italic;line-height:1.65;">"Mahathi gives your team the clarity to act on risk data in real time — cutting review cycles from days to hours."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice-card voice-dont">
        <div class="voice-card-label">✗ We Don't Say</div>
        <div class="voice-card-title">Jargon-Heavy</div>
        <p class="voice-card-body">We never lead with tech stacks, buzzwords, or vague transformation language that obscures meaning and loses executive audiences.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;padding:1rem;background:rgba(184,135,148,0.06);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);font-style:italic;line-height:1.65;text-decoration:line-through;opacity:0.7;">"Our AI-powered microservices leverage next-gen data pipelines for digital transformation."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice-card voice-do">
        <div class="voice-card-label">✓ We Say</div>
        <div class="voice-card-title">Precise & Direct</div>
        <p class="voice-card-body">We use specific, factual language. Numbers, timeframes, and concrete descriptions earn more trust than superlatives and hyperbole.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;padding:1rem;background:var(--cream);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--forest);font-style:italic;line-height:1.65;">"Built for enterprise scale — supporting 2M+ policies across 14 regulatory jurisdictions."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="voice-card voice-dont">
        <div class="voice-card-label">✗ We Don't Say</div>
        <div class="voice-card-title">Hyperbolic Claims</div>
        <p class="voice-card-body">We never claim to be "the best," "revolutionary," or "world-class" without evidence. Our authority comes from specificity, not superlatives.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:1rem;padding:1rem;background:rgba(184,135,148,0.06);border-radius:8px;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);font-style:italic;line-height:1.65;text-decoration:line-through;opacity:0.7;">"The world's most revolutionary insurance platform, disrupting the industry."</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Writing Principles -->
    <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Writing Principles</div>
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;"></div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.25rem;">
      <div style="background:var(--white);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--cream2);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Sentence Case</div>
        <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--forest);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Always use sentence case</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);line-height:1.65;">Capitalise the first word of a sentence and proper nouns only. Never use ALL CAPS for body text — reserve for display labels and DM Mono metadata only.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--cream2);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Active Voice</div>
        <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--forest);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Lead with action and clarity</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);line-height:1.65;">Write in active voice wherever possible. "Mahathi processes claims in hours" — not "Claims are processed in hours by Mahathi." Active voice signals confidence.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--cream2);padding:1.75rem;">
        <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">No Hyphenation</div>
        <div style="font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--forest);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Avoid line-break hyphenation</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--sage2);line-height:1.65;">Do not hyphenate words across lines in digital or print layouts. If text wraps awkwardly, adjust column width or rewrite the sentence. Widows and orphans should also be eliminated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

