  <section class="brand-section section-anchor" id="logo-usage">
    <div class="section-label">05 — Logo Rules</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Logo Do's &amp; Don'ts</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="section-intro">The Mahathi logo is a precision-built mark. Its integrity must be maintained across all applications. These rules are non-negotiable — they protect the brand's recognition, authority, and visual trust.</p>

    <div class="dos-donts-grid">
      <!-- DO 1 -->
      <div class="do-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:#ffffff">
          <span class="rule-badge badge-do">✓ Do</span>
          <img
          src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"
          alt="Mahathi logo"
          class="img-fluid"
          style="max-width:540px;width:100%;height:auto;"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="rule-meta">
          <div class="rule-title">Use on approved backgrounds</div>
          <div class="rule-desc">Always place the logo on Cream (#EEF0EC), Forest Green (#253830), or White. These are the only approved background surfaces.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- DO 2 -->
      <div class="do-card">
        <div class="rule-preview" style="background:#76A379;">
