    <p class="section-intro">Icons serve as quick-reference signifiers across digital platforms — navigation, status indicators, feature labels, and UI affordances. Mahathi uses a consistent, approved icon library that reflects the brand's precision and enterprise authority. Icons are always purposeful, never decorative.</p>

